                                                             <p class=\"mini-title s1\">Browser Compatibility<\/p>\n                    <p class=\"text s2\">\n                        A critical aspect of using Nexux is ensuring that you are utilizing a compatible web browser. It is important to\nenable JavaScript and allow cookies in your browser settings, as these are fundamental for our application to function correctly. If you\u2019re using an outdated version of any browser, you may encounter issues that can hinder your user experience. Additionally, if you are accessing our product from a corporate network, verify with your IT department that these browsers are supported to avoid any accessibility issues.                    <\/p>\n                    <ul class=\"benefit-list s1\">\n                        <li>\n<div class=\"icon\">\n<i class=\"icon-flare\"><\/i>\n<\/div>\n<p>\n<span> Google Chrome : <\/span>\nRecommended for the best performance. Ensure you are on\nthe latest <br>\nstable release.\n<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<div class=\"icon\">\n<i class=\"icon-flare\"><\/i>\n<\/div>\n<p>\n<span> Mozilla Firefox : <\/span>\nAlways keep it updated for enhanced security and\ncompatibility.\n<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<div class=\"icon\">\n<i class=\"icon-flare\"><\/i>\n<\/div>\n<p>\n<span> Microsoft Edge : <\/span>\nwith the latest version provides optimal compatibility.\n<\/p>\n<\/li>                    <\/ul>\n                                        <div class=\"entry-image s1 tf-hover\">\n                        <div class=\"hover-1\">\n                            <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/wpriverthemes.com\/nexux\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/article-detail-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"lazyload\">\n                        <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                                                            <p class=\"mini-title s1\">Internet Connection<\/p>\n                    <p class=\"text s2\">\n                        Our platform is optimized for modern operating systems, ensuring that users on Windows and macOS have a smooth experience. Additionally, consider the latency of your connection; a latency of below 50ms is preferred, especially\nfor real-time collaboration. If you frequently experience slow internet speeds, it may lead to delays in loading\ncontent or disrupted service. Testing your internet speed regularly can help ensure that you maintain a suitable connection for using our application.                    <\/p>\n                    <ul class=\"benefit-list s1\">\n                        <li>\n<div class=\"icon\">\n<i class=\"icon-flare\"><\/i>\n<\/div>\n<p>\n<span> Minimum Speed : <\/span>\nA stable internet connection with a minimum download\nspeed of 5 Mbps is suggested.\n<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<div class=\"icon\">\n<i class=\"icon-flare\"><\/i>\n<\/div>\n<p>\n<span> Optimal Speed : <\/span>\nfor features that require more bandwidth, a speed of 10\nMbps or higher is advisable.\n<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<div class=\"icon\">\n<i class=\"icon-flare\"><\/i>\n<\/div>\n<p>\n<span> Latency : <\/span>\nLower latency connections (below 50ms) are preferred for\nreal-time collaboration features.\n<\/p>\n<\/li>                    <\/ul>\n                                                            <p class=\"mini-title s1\">Security Settings<\/p>\n                    <p class=\"text s2\">\n                        Users operating in environments with heightened security measures, such as corporate networks, it is crucial to configure your security settings appropriately. Firewalls and antivirus software may inadvertently block access to Nexux leading to connectivity issues We recommend whitelisting our domain to prevent any disruption in service. If you are using a Virtual Private Network (VPN), be aware that while it enhances security, it can also introduce latency and may cause connectivity issues with our application. If you experience any disruptions while connected through a VPN, consider temporarily disabling it to see if that resolves the problem. Our commitment to\nsecurity is paramount, and we encourage users to maintain a secure environment while accessing our services.                    <\/p>\n                    <ul class=\"benefit-list s1\">\n                        <li>\n<div class=\"icon\">\n<i class=\"icon-flare\"><\/i>\n<\/div>\n<p>\n<span> Firewalls and Antivirus Software : <\/span>\nIf you are using firewalls or security software, make\nsure they do not block access to Nexus. You may need to\nadd our domain to a whitelist.\n<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<div class=\"icon\">\n<i class=\"icon-flare\"><\/i>\n<\/div>\n<p>\n<span> VPN Usage : <\/span>\nWhile using a VPN can enhance security, it may sometimes\ncause connectivity issues. If you experience problems,\nconsider temporarily disabling the VPN.\n<\/p>\n<\/li>                    <\/ul>\n                                        <div class=\"entry-image s1 tf-hover\">\n                        <div class=\"hover-1\">\n                            <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/wpriverthemes.com\/nexux\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/article-detail-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"lazyload\">\n                        <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                                                            <p class=\"mini-title s1\">Accessibility Features<\/p>\n                    <p class=\"text s2\">\n                        At Nexux we strive to ensure that our platform is accessible to all users. To enhance navigation, familiarize yourself\nwith the keyboard shortcuts available within the application. These shortcuts can significantly speed up your workflow and make it easier to access features without relying solely on mouse input. We encourage users to provide feedback on their experiences with accessibility features, as this helps us improve our platform continually. Your input is valuable in ensuring that we meet the needs of all users.                    <\/p>\n                    <ul class